Employee Andre Ross is no longer employed with SHYR  

All employees were trained on the appropriate use of EBI.  Our policy is clear on the justifiable reasons to utilize EBI:

1. A youth exhibits:
      a. self-injurious behavior that caused or is likely to cause injury;
      b. behavior which is likely to result in danger to self or others; and/or
      c. aggressive behavior that is likely to cause injury to others; and/or

2. A youth attempts to run away and may be a danger to self.

All employees are expected to adhere to the above policy. Failure to do so will result in Disciplinary Action. 
